                        <interp inst="t18660709-name-12" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM BELLABY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a labourer, living at 1, Gloucester Place—I was at work on Tower Hill on 21st June—I left my coat on the top of the pit, the sewer where I was at work—I next saw the coat in the con<lb></lb>stable's hand—it had been safe about five minutes before—this is the coat (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
               <p>
